      "text": [
        " قَالَ عَلِيٌّ صَلَوَاتُُ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ : \"مُبَاشَرَةُ اَلْمَرْأَةِ اِبْنَتَهَا إِذَا بَلَغَتْ سِتَّ سِنِينَ شُعْبَةٌ مِنَ اَلزِّنَا\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4505 - Muhammad ibn Yahya al-Khazzaz narrated from Ghiyath ibn Ibrahim, from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\n\"Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said: \"A woman touching her daughter in an inappropriate manner once she has reached six years of age is a form of indecency (a branch of fornication).\""
        ]
      }
    },
